  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b2bdc4a268c1abc4386e1f154d6bd7e5, type: 2}
  lines:
  - We are aware of how much you know
  - We have taken your daughter, and with it her life is in our hands.
  - If you wish to see her once more, hand us the information on what the spies have
    planned.
  - Do so and you and her both will be safely escorted away and your lifes spared.
  - Her fate is in your hands now, do not make the wrong choice.
